title: Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation
text:
> Top News Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation NFL Vice President International Mark Waller talks with reporters at the National Football League owners meeting, in New York, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015. The league's owners approved more international games through 2025 on Wednesday, including ones in places other than England — possibly Mexico, Germany and Canada.(AP Photo/Richard Drew) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
